umsebenzi wetrigonometric: Umsebenzi we-engile echazwe njengomlinganiselo wobude bamacala kanxantathu osekunene
umsebenzi ochaseneyo: Umsebenzi ofunyenwe ngokubonakalisa inguqu exhomekeke komnye umsebenzi njengoguquguquko oluzimeleyo komnye
i-cosecant: I-reciprocal of the sine function, echazwa njengomlinganiselo we hypotenuse ukuya kwelinye icala likanxantathu osekunene
i-cotangent: I-reciprocal of the tanjent function, ichazwa njengomlinganiselo wecala elimeleneyo likanxantathu oneengile ekunene.
identity trigonometric: Ukulingana okubandakanya imisebenzi yetrigonometric eyinyani kuwo onke amaxabiso eenguqu
umthetho wesines: Kunxantathu, umlinganiselo wobude becala ukuya kwisine ye-engile echaseneyo uhlala uhleli
umthetho we-cosines: Kunxantathu, isikwere secala silingana nenani lezikwere zamanye amacala amabini thabatha kabini imveliso yala macala mabini kunye ne-cosine ye-engile ebandakanyiweyo.
umlinganiselo weradian: Umlinganiselo we-engile kwiiradians, engumlinganiselo wobude be-arc kwiradiyasi yayo
ubude bearc: Umgama phakathi kwamanqaku amabini ecaleni kwecandelo legophe
icandelo: Isahlulo sesangqa esivalwe ngeeradiya ezimbini kunye ne-arc yabo edibeneyo
umlinganiselo wetrigonometric: Umlinganiselo wobude bamacala amabini kanxantathu wasekunene
inxaki yetrigonometric: Inxaki ebandakanya enye okanye imisebenzi emininzi yetrigonometric yoguquko
